name: Ronnie Coleman The King NFT Series

metadata.name: The King NFT #1
metadata.description: My record-tying 8th consecutive Olympia victory will always have a special place in my heart. Lee Haney was like an idol to me, and tying his record is something I never considered. I chose a Kings' costume because I felt my legacy would forever be cemented in history that night, and I was right. This is a super rare, one-of-a-kind piece of memorabilia that will be a prized collectible for years to come. I can't wait to personally meet the owner! - Ronnie Coleman
